{"id":340267,"date":[{"year":1957,"month":1,"day":9}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"104","ytitle":"","mtitle":"田野上飘浮着薄雾","ftitle":"","authors":["吴荫循"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"吴荫循"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田野上飘浮着薄雾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雾霭中走出一群少女。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她们走过碧绿的稻田，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"稻子正在灌浆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她们要到山上去砍柴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那山头还挂着月亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她们的笑声撒在田野，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"圆润清新如露珠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1956年9月-12月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陆丰-北京。"}]}